[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man in hospital after basement flat fire in Edinburgh

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has been taken to hospital following a fire in a basement flat in Edinburgh.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Firefighters were called to the scene in Queensferry Road at 05:46.
They put out the blaze in the flat and remained while the property was ventilated.
The condition of the man who was taken to Edinburgh Royal Infirmary is not known.
